      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the meat-free chick'n is browning, dissolve your<strong> tomato paste</strong> and <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[110ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>harissa stock</strong></p><p>Once the meat-free chick'n has browned, reduce the heat to medium and add the <strong>harissa stock</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min, until the meat-free chick'n is warmed through and the stock has reduced</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
