      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, combine your <strong>vegan mayo</strong> with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up until it's smooth – this is your <strong>lemony dressing</strong></p>",
