    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free chick'n is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks - this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Return the <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> to the pan with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully coated in the sauce</p>",
